{"tid":1537623,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"國際文宣：港澳辦,中聯辦,中央破壞香港法治","createTime":"2019-09-04T03:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T05:26:40.000Z","uid":210755,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"21ba40faa5b821a56f09ae16b995080569103816","tid":1537623,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:51:01.000Z","msg":"係人都知林鄭係扯線公仔,雖然佢都係千古罪人<br />\n但背後下指令嘅港澳辦,中聯辦,中央躲後面推哂比林鄭拖字訣，中央話咩&quot;相信港府有能力解決香港困局, 對香港依法施政&quot;<br />\n但實情港府根本無權力回應市民<br />\n<br />\n港澳辦,中聯辦,中央一直唔肯授權香港聆聽幾百萬市民嘅民意；違反國家憲法 權力不在人民；違反基本法 剝奪香港市民普選權利；<br />\n<br />\no係合法性上,當年若果唔係承諾普選 香港根本唔會肯回歸, 咁樣係唔合法統治香港<br />\n<br />\n港澳辦,中聯辦,中央不斷從干擾香港法治,國教，教學語言 ，種族清洗 香港無審批權每日150, 政治審判 etc  要佢地成為全球國際輿論壓力焦點先有用,強調佢地強壞香港<br />\n<br />\n有普選先會令香港經濟更繁榮昌盛 塊餅越來越大,仲可以還富於民"},{"pid":"b6da5e6cc2d6deea327be942e011dfad6c16eef3","tid":1537623,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:51:20.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38c3d0b37c3b035e3f957effb12a8bea4029043a","tid":1537623,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/biantailajiaomanhua/btlj-09032019163817.html/1/@@images/f869f51c-7a83-4734-b98f-0250d65829fe.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fbiantailajiaomanhua%2Fbtlj-09032019163817.html%2F1%2F%40%40images%2Ff869f51c-7a83-4734-b98f-0250d65829fe.jpeg&h=f139eaa9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c37dc96eb944b2f16e8e944242235b58d10861f","tid":1537623,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}